📄 Project Overview
The Salon Management System is a web-based application designed to streamline and automate salon operations. It helps manage appointments, services, staff schedules, and client records efficiently.
⚙️ Tech Stack
Programming Languages:HTML, CSS,JavaScript, PHP
Database: MySQL
🚀 Features
Appointment Scheduling: Book, update, and cancel client appointments.
Service Management: Add and remove salon services with pricing details.
Client Records: Store and manage client information and visit history.
Staff Management: Assign shifts and roles to employees.
Reporting: Generate daily and monthly reports on services offered and income


Project link: https://github.com/odongograce/odongograce.github.io
